name: THE WARRIOR
description:
Protector of Olympus and the armies

Lord of bloody war and cruelty

Personifies the fury of war, the brutality and the horrors of battle

Symbol of courage and strength
God of male virility

The most unpopular of all the Gods of Olympus for his explosive temperament, aggressiveness and insatiable thirst for conflict

The sacker of cities, He’s ARES
